Payment and game activity will be void in the event of a malfunction

CREDIT indicates the amount of credit available
according to the COIN VALUE you choose.
BALANCE indicates the amount of real money available.
BET indicates the amount that you will bet on the next spin.
WIN indicates the amount won in the previous game
and is already multiplied by the selected coin value.

1.Select the COIN VALUE that you want to use.
2.This game is a MEGAWAYS™ slot with up to 117,649 winning ways.
3.Each spin will cost 20 x selected coin value.
4.Press on SPIN to start the game.
5.Use AUTO SPIN to set your own automatic play settings.
6. Only the highest win per line is awarded.

 All winnings are paid from left to right except for SCATTERS.
THE WINNING SYMBOL PAYOUT IS MULTIPLIED BY THE NUMBER OF WINNING WAYS TO GIVE THE TOTAL WIN:
MULTIPLY THE NUMBER OF ADJACENT WINNING SYMBOLS ON EACH OF THE REELS TO GIVE THE TOTAL NUMBER OF WINNING WAYS … IN THE ABOVE EXAMPLE YOU HAVE 12:
Combinaisons dont les gains peuvent être générés à partir de plusieurs symboles à chaque tour & cascade.
Wins are awarded on left to right adjacent symbols regardless of size. Payouts are multiplied by stake.
Each spin can have up to 117,649 ways to win!

Get 5 Gold Scatters to trigger the Aztec Gold Cash Respins feature.
Start with 3 Cash Respins and if another Scatter lands in view the number of respins will reset to 3.Watch out for the Mini, Major and Mega Scatters for even bigger wins.Fill an entire reel to activate the multiplier for all Scatters on that reel.
When the Cash Respins end all Scatter values in view will be paid.
Every winning symbol is part of a reaction and is replaced by cascading symbols from above the reels.

Payouts shown are in coins.
All payouts will be multiplied by the selected coin value.
Wild substitutes for all symbols except Scatter
5 or more Scatters trigger Cash Respins
